This program is meant to count the order of red zones and the current red zone.
When a zone that isn't yours is active, the text will turn green.
When a zone that is yours is active, the text will flash red and blue.
When there are no zones active, the text will display the current/past zone number and corresponding class.

This program works with the following settings:
Resolution: 1920x1080
Game Quality: Low
Monster Animations: Disabled
Player Animations: Disabled
Damage Numbers: Enabled or Disabled
Monster: Hide or Show
Smooth Background: On

Changes to these settings may affect the functionality of the program. Change at your own risk.